<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>上半年营收为3.84亿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200928/150f70e86d1849d59c3e96c3e667a80c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
